utils.cmd.calc.help:
§e.calc §dcalc §b<expression>§r - Evaluates the expression and returns the result
§e.calc §dcraft §b<item> <expression>§r - calculate how many materials you need to craft some item.
§e.calc §d(nether|overworld) §a[x y z]§r - calculate what the coordinates would be in the specified dimension. Uses the player's coordinates by default.
§e.calc §dcustom add §e<name> <arguments...> §r= §b<expression>§r - add a custom function you can invoke that evaluates to some expression.
§e.calc §dcustom remove §e<name>§r - remove a custom function
§e.calc §dcustom list§r - list all the currently defined custom functions.
utils.cmd.cosmetics.help: §e.cosmetics§r - Opens the cosmetics screen; Does nothing if you're not connected to a service server.
